any_property_closely_inherited.question_number = Question 6
any_property_closely_inherited.browser_title = Question page
any_property_closely_inherited.title = Does any part of the property that you have just given the value of pass to a direct descendant or their spouse or civil partner?
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance = A person’s direct descendant is:
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet1 = a child, grandchild or great grandchild, including any of their children
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet2 = the spouse or civil partner of a child, grandchild or great grandchild, including any of their children
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet3 = a widow, widower or surviving civil partner of a child, grandchild or great grandchild, including any of their children
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet4 = a child who is, or was at any part of their life, their step-child
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet5 = an adopted child
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet6 = a child who they fostered at any time
any_property_closely_inherited.guidance.bullet7 = a child who they were appointed as a guardian or special guardian of when that child was under 18
